query:
-- Buscar todos os testes psicométricos concluídos
SELECT 
  pt.id,
  pt.testType,
  pt.employeeId,
  e.name as employeeName,
  e.registration as employeeRegistration,
  pt.completedAt,
  pt.createdAt,
  CASE 
    WHEN pt.responses IS NOT NULL THEN 'completed'
    ELSE 'pending'
  END as status
FROM psychometricTests pt
LEFT JOIN employees e ON pt.employeeId = e.id
WHERE pt.completedAt IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY pt.completedAt DESC
LIMIT 50;
